{"tid":2337378,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10.1串謀暴動案審結 押後至2月19日裁決","createTime":"2020-12-23T08:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T11:07:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63e634be08b8e344eb2e4d611c0ecf315e609f42","tid":2337378,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12375&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp7O6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=fdf10163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12375</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅六庭<br />\n#沈小民法官<br />\n#1001銅鑼灣 #續審 [15/18] <br />\n<br />\nA1: 張 (23)  A2: 胡 (21)<br />\nA3: 陳 (21)  A4: 蘇 (25)<br />\nA5: 李 (17)  A6: 沈 (24) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：串謀參與暴動<br />\n被控於2019年9月28日至10月1日，與不知名人士串謀參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n交替控罪：串謀參與非法集結<br />\n被控於同日同地與不知名人士串謀參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n背景：10月1日各區遍地開花，警方當日凌晨根據線報，到銅鑼灣一個單位內拘捕多人，搜出白電油、玻璃瓶、布條、防毒面具等物品。A1先被控串謀暴動，及後才修改為串謀縱火，延至開審控方才改控眾被告串謀參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n所有辯方律師結案陳詞完畢<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年2月19日1400區域法院裁決，期間各被告以現有條件保釋。"},{"pid":"a8624ae6e315a56cbd57968827ce96eb5605c2cb","tid":2337378,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480c396077c2dc46c1289b3c9a6aee31096bba34","tid":2337378,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4582da2392c5e7cb79aea3d9662d56e3be9ff7a","tid":2337378,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8624ae6e315a56cbd57968827ce96eb5605c2cb","tid":2337378,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23